  {"id":"mississippi","nameZh":"密西西比河","nameEn":"Mississippi River","category":"river","country":"美國","lat":34.0,"lng":-91.0,"region":"北美中央平原","summary":"北美洲最重要的河川系統之一，向南流入墨西哥灣。","formation":"河川匯集廣大中央平原的地表水，長期搬運沉積物並塑造氾濫平原與三角洲。","features":["廣大流域","航運與農業","氾濫平原與三角洲"],"question":"密西西比河為什麼適合發展內河航運？","maps":"https://www.google.com/maps/search/?api=1&query=Mississippi+River","video":"https://www.youtube.com/results?search_query=Mississippi+River+NOAA+education","official":"https://www.noaa.gov/","sourceNote":"河流線為教學概略化；可延伸查閱 NOAA 與 USGS 水文資料。"},
  {"id":"colorado-river","nameZh":"科羅拉多河","nameEn":"Colorado River","category":"river","country":"美國、墨西哥","lat":36.1,"lng":-112.1,"region":"科羅拉多高原與乾燥西南部","summary":"切割科羅拉多高原並形成大峽谷，也是美國西南部重要水源。","formation":"高原抬升後，河流長期向下切蝕岩層，形成深峽谷。","features":["大峽谷","水壩與水庫","跨州與跨國水資源"],"question":"河流侵蝕與地殼抬升如何共同形成大峽谷？","maps":"https://www.google.com/maps/search/?api=1&query=Colorado+River","video":"https://www.youtube.com/results?search_query=Colorado+River+Grand+Canyon+NPS+geology","official":"https://www.nps.gov/grca/learn/nature/geologicformations.htm","sourceNote":"地質說明以 Grand Canyon NPS 官方頁面為延伸來源。"},
  {"id":"mackenzie","nameZh":"馬更些河","nameEn":"Mackenzie River","category":"river","country":"加拿大","lat":65.2,"lng":-127.5,"region":"加拿大西北部","summary":"加拿大重要北流河川，最終注入北冰洋。","formation":"匯集大奴湖及加拿大西北部水系，流經凍土與寒帶地區。","features":["向北冰洋排水","季節性結冰","大型三角洲"],"question":"春季由南向北融冰時，為什麼容易發生冰塞洪水？","maps":"https://www.google.com/maps/search/?api=1&query=Mackenzie+River","video":"https://www.youtube.com/results?search_query=Mackenzie+River+Canada+geography","official":"https://natural-resources.canada.ca/","sourceNote":"延伸資料可查 Natural Resources Canada。"},
